PhotoCell - Class in models
In order to display the images inside the table columns in Album Overview and search we set each cell of the table column to display a custom anchor pane that holds an ImageView where we put the image stored within the serialized image field in photo its used in 2 different tables so its best to just make it its own object and use it in both controllers
